{
  "texts": [
    "• We employ a suite of tools in FinAgent, including expert guidance and technical indicator-based advanced trading strategies, to infuse domain knowledge in financial trading.With comprehensive experiments on 6 financial datasets, including stocks and Crypto, FinAgent significantly outperforms 12 stateof-the-art baselines in terms of 6 financial metrics with over 36% average improvement on profit.",
    "Specifically, a 92.27% return (a 84.39% relative improvement) is achieved on one dataset.",
    "Notably, FinAgent is the first advanced multimodal foundation agent designed for financial trading tasks.",
    "RELATED WORK 2.1 LLM Agents for Decision MakingThe field of artificial intelligence and natural language processing has reached a significant milestone with the emergence of LLMs like ChatGPT [23] and GPT-4 [24].",
    "BloombergGPT [47] introduced the first LLM in the finance domain, combining financial and text data, but without public access."
  ]
}